title: ‘Salt Lake City’ Episode 1 and ‘Beverly Hills’ Episode 20
description:
Rachel kicks off this week’s 'Morally Corrupt' with a bit of our own Bravo news, before diving into the Season 3 premiere of ‘The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City’ with Chelsea Stark-Jones (11:48). Then, Rachel is joined by Jodi Walker to break down Season 12, Episode 20 of ‘The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills’ (38:25).
Host: Rachel Lindsay
Guest: Chelsea Stark-Jones and Jodi Walker
Producers: Devon Manze
Theme Song: Devon Renaldo
